      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software quality assurance procedures documented and verified for MRL 5; version control, regression testing, and audit trails required.",
      "rationale": "Basic version control is in place but regression test suite covers only 40% of solver modules. Audit trails are incomplete. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4 for Class III device at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method of manufactured solutions applied to all governing equations relevant to hemolysis prediction.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing performed on Navier-Stokes solver only; hemolysis transport equation not independently verified. Achieved level 2 insufficient for MRL 5 requirement of level 4."
    },
    {
