      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match VAD operating envelope including fluid temperature, hematocrit, and rotational speed to within specified tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data sourced from FDA generic pump study; hematocrit controlled but fluid temperature varied by ±3°C from nominal. Rotational speed uncertainty not fully characterized. Achieved level 3 below required level 5."
