      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E% or validation metric u_val) computed for hemolysis index at all operating points with uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "Validation metric computed at 3 of 5 operating points. Uncertainty bounds on experimental hemolysis measurements not available for remaining 2 points. Achieved level 3 versus required level 5."
