      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for selection of turbulence model, hemolysis damage accumulation model, and constitutive relations; sensitivity to model form choices quantified.",
      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model selected without comparative evaluation against Lagrangian or strain-based alternatives. Turbulence model sensitivity not assessed. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level 1."
