      "acceptanceCriteria": "Uncertainty in all model inputs (fluid viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients, boundary conditions) propagated through Monte Carlo UQ to hemolysis index output.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ framework established but hemolysis model coefficients (C and alpha exponents) treated as deterministic. Input uncertainty for inlet velocity profile not characterized. Achieved level 1."
