      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test samples must be representative of production VAD units; sample-to-sample variability characterized and accounted for in validation comparisons.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump data derived from a single pump unit. Sample-to-sample manufacturing variability not characterized. No information on blood sample donor variability. Epistemic gap; achieved level 1."
