    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged under ASME V&V 40 framework. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors identified as epistemic gaps at Model Risk Level 5. Despite gaps, the package is accepted for submission pending remediation plan. Monte Carlo UQ framework provides partial uncertainty characterization sufficient for current regulatory interaction.",
